SWITCHES
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
START        Click here to play the game

HELP ON/OFF  Enable/disable use of the help-mode in the game. With HELP ON you
             will have 3 available help for each level but a lower bonus-score
             at the end of the game

TIME ON/OFF  Enable/disable the time-limit in the game. With TIME ON you will
             achieve higher scores

ABOUT        Some infos about the authors

HIGH-SCORES  Display the high-scores screen

QUIT         Guess what?




